NO X-FACTOR

There is no point wasting energy mourning the fact Suarez is no longer at Anfield but it is impossible not to see that Liverpool are now easy to play against without him.

When Suarez was leading the line, Liverpool had intensity. He scrambled the minds of defenders, created space for other to cause havoc and his presence in the team dragged his colleagues up another level.

